    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's helpful. i also saw something in my textbook about how the reaction can sometimes happen too fast or cause weird flavors if the moisture levels aren't right. is there a way to describe the 'magic' of how these molecules actually transform into those new flavors? it's hard to visualize the actual transition.",
